<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 12:14:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登：如果没有以色列，世界上每个犹太人都将面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/biden-without-israel-every-jew-in-the-world-would-be-at-risk/00000190-bac9-d458-a3d7-bbefa3f00000</link><description>拜登加强了对以色列的立场，称自己是犹太复国主义者。 “你不必是犹太人才能成为犹太复国主义者，”他在周一的采访中说。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/biden-without-israel-every-jew-in-the-world-would-be-at-risk/00000190-bac9-d458-a3d7-bbefa3f00000</guid></item><item><title>有一段时间，加沙人希望战争能够结束。现在他们感觉自己被抛弃了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/for-a-moment-gazans-had-hope-the-war-would-end-now-they-feel-theyve-been-abandoned/00000190-bab2-d211-a5da-fffb31440000</link><description>加沙人民说，世界只关心穆罕默德·德伊夫发生了什么，“没有人再谈论数十名死者了”。一位人权活动人士表示，过去曾有国际压力，但“现在，每个人都在等待内塔尼亚胡”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/for-a-moment-gazans-had-hope-the-war-would-end-now-they-feel-theyve-been-abandoned/00000190-bab2-d211-a5da-fffb31440000</guid></item><item><title>阻止向加沙提供援助的极右团体获得美国和以色列的免税捐款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/far-right-groups-blocking-aid-to-gaza-receive-tax-deductible-donations-from-us-and-israel/00000190-ba8f-db47-abb0-baffc7370000</link><description>尽管受到制裁，三个极端民族主义团体仍从美国和以色列收到了超过 20 万美元的免税捐款。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 09:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/far-right-groups-blocking-aid-to-gaza-receive-tax-deductible-donations-from-us-and-israel/00000190-ba8f-db47-abb0-baffc7370000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易的框架仍然存在。细节等待以色列领导人的意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/a-framework-for-a-hostage-deal-still-exists-the-details-await-israels-leaders-input/00000190-ba57-d458-a3d7-bbf7ad6a0000</link><description>现在重要的问题不是哈马斯领导人穆罕默德·德伊夫是生还是死，而是谈判将会发生什么。僵局可能会持续到美国大选，从而进一步危及人质的生命安全，并大大增加以色列和黎巴嫩之间爆发全面战争的可能性</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/a-framework-for-a-hostage-deal-still-exists-the-details-await-israels-leaders-input/00000190-ba57-d458-a3d7-bbf7ad6a0000</guid></item><item><title>三名军官和一名哲学家：决定谁是依良心拒服兵役者的秘密以色列国防军委员会内部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-officers-and-a-philosopher-inside-the-secretive-idf-conscience-committee/00000190-b619-df08-a9fe-f7d9b7c10000</link><description>人权倡导者表示，根据以色列国防军对该术语的定义，即使是马丁·路德·金和圣雄甘地也不会被视为良心拒服兵役者。委员会中的学者、活动人士、反对者和律师告诉《国土报》，军事系统如何应对挑衅的拒绝者</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-officers-and-a-philosopher-inside-the-secretive-idf-conscience-committee/00000190-b619-df08-a9fe-f7d9b7c10000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太艺术家对美化哈马斯大屠杀的艺术作品感到愤怒，感到沉默和疏远</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</link><description>当纽约一个著名的文化空间向一位艺术家展示其橱窗并对哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击表示赞赏时，许多犹太和以色列艺术家感到震惊，但并不完全感到惊讶。正如一位策展人所指责的那样，艺术界是否创造了“一个从单一角度看待现实的平坦领域”？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡命令以色列军队在10月7日之后关闭会议录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ordered-israeli-army-to-turn-off-recording-of-meetings-after-october-7/00000190-b7ef-db47-abb0-bfffd0900000</link><description>通常情况下，录音系统是自动运行的，记录陆军总部指挥中心发生的一切，但战争一开始，总理就下令关闭所有录音。军队遵守了这个命令</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ordered-israeli-army-to-turn-off-recording-of-meetings-after-october-7/00000190-b7ef-db47-abb0-bfffd0900000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙作战，10 月 7 日炮击基布兹房屋的以色列国防军坦克军官表示“我别无选择”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-in-gaza-idf-officer-who-shelled-a-kibbutz-house-on-october-7-has-no-regrets/00000190-b806-db47-abb0-ba77d8b20000</link><description>10月7日，尼西姆·哈赞上校控制了一辆受损的坦克，并将其开往贝埃里基布兹，在那里他与哈马斯恐怖分子进行了整整两天的战斗。正是在那里，他向佩西·科恩的家发射了一枚炮弹。他告诉《国土报》，他不知道里面有人质。 “那天我们需要改变现状，”他说</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-in-gaza-idf-officer-who-shelled-a-kibbutz-house-on-october-7-has-no-regrets/00000190-b806-db47-abb0-ba77d8b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因涉嫌为伊朗工作而被捕；加沙人报告以色列国防军空袭造成数十人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-live/barrage-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-after-three-killed-in-lebanon-airstrike/00000190-b936-db47-abb0-bb77e2b30000</link><description>哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部称，昨天有 49 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙地带丧生 ■ 加沙边境社区启动火箭警报 ■ 以色列人因涉嫌与伊朗情报部门接触而被捕 ■ 巴勒斯坦报道：以色列国防军与巴拉塔难民营武装分子交火, 约旦河西岸 ■ 以色列边境警察在约旦河西岸持刀袭击中受轻伤 ■ 周一晚间，以色列北部城镇遭到 20 枚火箭弹发射</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-live/barrage-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-after-three-killed-in-lebanon-airstrike/00000190-b936-db47-abb0-bb77e2b30000</guid></item><item><title>JD万斯在当选特朗普副总统后首次发表讲话，敦促以色列“尽快”结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/j-d-vance-trumps-vp-pick-urges-israel-to-finish-gaza-war-as-quick-as-possible/00000190-b947-da51-a19a-fdef7b240000</link><description>这位俄亥俄州参议员曾写道，特朗普可能是“美国的希特勒”，他指责拜登总统“让以色列越来越难赢得这场战争”，并发誓要“重振以色列和沙特阿拉伯之间的和平进程”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:24:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/j-d-vance-trumps-vp-pick-urges-israel-to-finish-gaza-war-as-quick-as-possible/00000190-b947-da51-a19a-fdef7b240000</guid></item><item><title>报道：国防部长加兰特告诉人质家属“以色列有史以来最接近达成协议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</link><description>据以色列第 12 频道援引未透露姓名的消息人士的报道，10 月 7 日，国防部长约夫·加兰特在会见在军事基地被绑架的以色列国防军女观察员家属时，暗示与哈马斯的人质谈判取得了重大进展</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家解释为什么斯德泰曼拘留设施不依法运作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</link><description>该国表示打算将被拘留者转移到以色列其他监狱或将他们送回加沙，但此后一再要求推迟。在该州再次要求推迟后，法官要求政府在 10 天内做出回应</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</guid></item><item><title>2014年，以色列与哈马斯开战。十年后，我们正经历着残酷的重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</link><description>我们已经用十年的时间从​​ 2014 年发生的事件中汲取教训，其中许多事件似乎预示着即将发生的事情。这一次，没有任何借口让加沙恢复现状——我们已经看到，这对于以色列人和巴勒斯坦人来说是多么不可持续和危险</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士称，试图杀死德伊夫损害了与哈马斯的停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</link><description>一位以色列消息人士表示，“事情并没有像往常一样进行。”一位政府消息人士称，“哈马斯遭受了严重打击，他们对这一事件的反应非常软弱，近乎无反应。”结果，摩萨德主任尚未启程前往卡塔尔进行谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯人和巴勒斯坦人谴责以色列对“安全”区哈马斯指挥官的不作为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/arabs-and-palestinians-decry-inaction-over-israel-targeting-hamas-commander-in-safe-zone/00000190-b6a2-d64e-a1d7-f7e677d30000</link><description>在以色列对本应安全的地区进行大规模轰炸后，以色列阿拉伯城市的抗议者集会“声援加沙人民”，而整个阿拉伯世界的许多人则在社交媒体上指责他们的政府缺乏保护。结束战争的努力</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/arabs-and-palestinians-decry-inaction-over-israel-targeting-hamas-commander-in-safe-zone/00000190-b6a2-d64e-a1d7-f7e677d30000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟制裁以色列极右翼领导人、极端主义定居者团体和前哨基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/european-union-sanctions-israeli-far-right-leaders-extremist-settler-groups-and-outposts/00000190-b77d-d3a7-a79e-f77f7d000000</link><description>以色列担心，在国际法院就以色列占领西岸是否符合国际法的合法性作出裁决后，对与西岸定居点有关的实体和个人实施的日益严厉的制裁将会加剧</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/european-union-sanctions-israeli-far-right-leaders-extremist-settler-groups-and-outposts/00000190-b77d-d3a7-a79e-f77f7d000000</guid></item><item><title>报告：与叙利亚阿萨德有联系的商人在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/report-businessman-with-ties-to-syrias-assad-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike/00000190-b795-de8b-adfc-bfb525fa0000</link><description>据报道，与真主党有经济联系、此前曾受到美国制裁的巴拉·卡特吉(Baraa Katerji)在袭击中身亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/report-businessman-with-ties-to-syrias-assad-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike/00000190-b795-de8b-adfc-bfb525fa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战，第 283 天：以色列国防军袭击加沙中部南部；欧盟制裁以色列极右活动人士和实体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-283-idf-strikes-gaza-eu-sanctions-far-right-israeli-activists/00000190-b74a-db47-abb0-bf7b65240000</link><description>在哈马斯发表相互矛盾的声明后，以色列官员表示，达成协议的谈判仍在继续。 ■ 以色列国防军袭击加沙南部和中部，试图对哈马斯施加更大压力。 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡就煽动反对他的问题举行会议后，反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德表示：“内塔尼亚胡不是一个受害者;他是个爱发牢骚的人，也是个胆小鬼。 ■ 欧盟对五名以色列极右活动分子和三个实体实施制裁 ■ 战争进入 283 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-283-idf-strikes-gaza-eu-sanctions-far-right-israeli-activists/00000190-b74a-db47-abb0-bf7b65240000</guid></item><item><title>亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡在人质交易关键时刻批评卡塔尔后引发新争议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/yair-netanyahu-sparks-fresh-controversy-after-criticizing-qatar-at-key-hostage-deal-moment/00000190-b71b-d5a5-af99-ff1b20b40000</link><description>据瓦拉报道，他在迈阿密举行的一次会议上表示，卡塔尔是“仅次于伊朗的世界第二大恐怖主义资助者”，并声称他们资助反以色列校园抗议活动。卡塔尔一名官员驳斥了这些说法，称其为“无稽之谈”，并表示这可能会使人质谈判“复杂化”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/yair-netanyahu-sparks-fresh-controversy-after-criticizing-qatar-at-key-hostage-deal-moment/00000190-b71b-d5a5-af99-ff1b20b40000</guid></item><item><title>Wiz 做什么？谷歌将如何从此次收购中受益？这对以色列意味着什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/what-does-wiz-do-how-will-google-benefit-and-what-does-it-mean-for-israel/00000190-b6f0-d8f7-add0-f7faf2270000</link><description>如果这家以色列网络安全公司确实被美国科技巨头以 230 亿美元收购，这将标志着以色列经济的一个里程碑。它的创始人和员工会赚多少钱，它将如何影响云计算，以及以色列将从销售中获得多少税收？</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/what-does-wiz-do-how-will-google-benefit-and-what-does-it-mean-for-israel/00000190-b6f0-d8f7-add0-f7faf2270000</guid></item></channel></rss>